學者一般將假定的[[原始印歐人|原始印歐人]]同[[Y染色体|Y染色体]][[单倍型类群|单倍型类群]][[单倍型类群R-M420|R1a1]]相關聯，在歐洲主要出現在[[東歐|東歐]]和[[中歐|中歐]]。在歐洲還有與其親緣最近的[[Y染色体|Y染色体]][[单倍型类群|单倍型类群]][[单倍型类群R1b_(Y-DNA)|R1b]]，在[[新石器時代|新石器時代]]隨農耕技術而從[[近東|近東]]傳入<ref>Balaresque et al. 2010, [http://www.plosbiology.org/article/info:doi/10.1371/journal.pbio.1000285 A Predominantly Neolithic Origin for European Paternal Lineages] {{Wayback|url=http://www.plosbiology.org/article/info:doi/10.1371/journal.pbio.1000285 |date=20101205010728 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/science/2010/jan/19/british-men-ancient-farmers Most British men are descended from ancient farmers] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/science/2010/jan/19/british-men-ancient-farmers |date=20130722212421 }}, [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]], 20 January 2010<br />[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/8467623.stm Most European males 'descended from farmers'] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/8467623.stm |date=20110512161342 }}, [[BBC_News|BBC News]], 20 January 2010<br />[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-1244654/Study-finds-Britons-descended-farmers-left-Iraq-Syria-10-000-years-ago.html Study finds Britons are descended from farmers who left Iraq and Syria 10,000 years ago] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-1244654/Study-finds-Britons-descended-farmers-left-Iraq-Syria-10-000-years-ago.html |date=20131230223040 }}, [[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]], 20 January 2010</ref>，與[[西歐|西歐]][[凱爾特人|凱爾特人]]相關。

